suppressMessages(library(Seurat))
suppressMessages(library(ggplot2))
shiny <- readRDS("/mnt/scratch/home/marta/shiny/ageing-muscle/datasets/muscle_after_norm_none.rds")
t_cells <- shiny$clusters$clusters_0.2
t_cells <- t_cells == 6 & shiny$variables_df$condition == "Old"
tcell_mat <- t(shiny$matrix)[,t_cells]
tcell_mat[1:5,1:5]

tcell_tsne <- shiny$dimRed_list$tsne[t_cells,]
tcell_tsne[1:5,]
matrix <- tcell_mat["Cd4",]
matrix[1:5]
## ACACTGAAGTGTACCT-1 AGAGCAGCACCAACAT-1 AGCCACGAGCCACCGT-1 ATGGTTGGTCGCAGTC-1 
##           1.186165           2.179234           1.946337           1.061999 
## CAGATTGAGGCTAGCA-1 
##           0.000000
new_order <- order(matrix, decreasing = FALSE)

reduced <- tcell_tsne[new_order,]
reduced[1:5,]
matrix <- matrix[new_order]

df <- data.frame(dim_1 = reduced$dim_1, dim_2 = reduced$dim_2, exp = matrix)

ggplot(data = df, aes(x = dim_1, y = dim_2, color = exp)) + geom_point() +
    xlab("Dim_1") +
    ylab("Dim_2") +
    scale_colour_gradient(low = "gray88", high = "red" ) + labs(color = "Cd4")  +
    theme(text = element_text(size=15), 
          panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
          panel.background = element_blank(), axis.line = element_line(colour = "black")) + ggtitle("Old")
